Queen - Bohemian Rhapsody
Released 20/11/1975
#Queen #bohemianrhapsody #rock #rockandroll #indie #alternativo 

🌅 Imagen de fondo: https://mx.pinterest.com/pin/455356212344521625/

🍃 Sígueme a mí (chi?)
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/richii.almazan/
Canal Principal:
____________________________________

Lyrics de la canción :D
[Intro]
Is this the real life? Is this just fantasy?
Caught in a landslide, no escape from reality
Open your eyes, look up to the skies and see
I'm just a poor boy, I need no sympathy (Ooh, poor boy)
Because I'm easy come, easy go, little high, little low
Any way the wind blows (Ooh, the wind blows)
Doesn't really matter to me, to me

[Verse 1]
Mama, just killed a man
Put a gun against his head, pulled my trigger, now he's dead
Mama, life had just begun
But now I've gone and thrown it all away
Mama, ooh, didn't mean to make you cry
If I'm not back again this time tomorrow
Carry on, carry on as if nothing really matters

[Verse 2]
Too late, my time has come
Sends shivers down my spine, body's aching all the time
Goodbye, everybody, I've got to go
Gotta leave you all behind and face the truth
Mama, ooh (Any way the wind blows)
I don't wanna die (Ooh)
I sometimes wish I'd never been born at all (Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh)

[Guitar Solo]

[Verse 3]
I see a little silhouetto of a man
Scaramouche, Scaramouche, will you do the Fandango?
Thunderbolt and lightning, very, very frightening me
(Galileo) Galileo, (Galileo) Galileo, Galileo Figaro
Magnifico (Oh-oh-oh-oh)
But I'm just a poor boy, nobody loves me
He's just a poor boy from a poor family
Spare him his life from this monstrosity
Easy come, easy go, will you let me go?
Bismillah, no, we will not let you go (Let him go)
Bismillah, we will not let you go (Let him go)
Bismillah, we will not let you go (Let me go)
Will not let you go (Let me go)
(Never, never, never, never, never, never let me go) Will not let you go
Oh-oh-oh-oh
No, no, no, no, no, no, no
Oh, mamma mia, mamma mia (Mamma mia, let me go)
Beelzebub has a devil put aside for me, for me, for me

[Bridge]
So you think you can stone me and spit in my eye?
So you think you can love me and leave me to die?
Oh, baby, can't do this to me, baby
Just gotta get out, just gotta get right outta here
[Outro]
(Ooh)
(Ooh, yeah, ooh, yeah)
Nothing really matters, anyone can see
Nothing really matters
Nothing really matters to me
Any way the wind blows

snippet.title: KUMA | Bande-annonce 02 ÉP 41 | Sol Yanım (Doublé en Français) @araftadizisi
snippet.description:
Kuma | Bande-annonce 02 de l’Épisode 41 (Doublé en Français)
Full Episode → https://youtu.be/TJCEcXb5lck

Abonnez-vous aujourd’hui et plongez dans l’univers de Kuma ! → 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFfH8yBcEGg57loh1b07vGg?sub_confirmation=1

Un nouvel indice rouvre l’enquête et Karan retrouve l’espoir d’innocenter Ceylan. Entre un petit jeu complice et une surprise d’anniversaire en secret, les cœurs se rapprochent pendant que la famille s’en mêle. L’amour trébuche, se relève et réclame la confiance. Vous êtes dans quel camp—Karan & Ceylan ou le tumulte familial ?

À 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐏𝐎𝐒 𝐃𝐄 𝐊𝐔𝐌𝐀

Amour ou vengeance ? Les deux ont un prix…💔

Ceylan, une mariée en fuite, échappe à sa famille impitoyable et trouve refuge — ainsi qu’une passion électrique — dans les bras de Karan Çelikhan, héritier d’une puissante dynastie. Mais alors que leur romance secrète s’enflamme, un événement tragique fait tout basculer. Coincés entre amour et vengeance, ils doivent affronter des traditions brutales, des secrets familiaux enfouis, et un destin au lourd tribut. 

🔔 Kuma est disponible en exclusivité sur notre chaîne YouTube officielle ➤
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFfH8yBcEGg57loh1b07vGg?sub_confirmation=1

Portée par Aybüke Yılmaz et Emre Özmen, cette série met en scène un duel bouleversant entre amour, haine et destin. Grâce à son rythme haletant et son intrigue percutante, Kuma captivera les spectateurs semaine après semaine.

≫ Produite par Stellar Yapım, GoQuest Media & VIP 2000
≫ Créatrice de la série : İnci Gülen Oarr
≫ Réalisation : Atilla Cengiz & Irmak Çengel
≫ Directeurs de la photographie : Sinan Onur & Ferhat Özyurt
≫ Musique : Saki Cimen
≫ Scénario : Ahmet Köseoğlu & Gökçen Eroğlu

𝐃𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐩𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐚𝐥𝐞:

Emre Özmen dans le rôle de Karan (rôle principal masculin)
Aybüke Yılmaz dans le rôle de Ceylan (rôle principal féminin)
Hilal Tüfek dans le rôle de Sema (épouse de Salih, belle-sœur de Karan)
Ufuk Kaplan dans le rôle de Kudret Çelikhan (mère de Karan et Salih) 

𝐃𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐒𝐞𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐞:

≫ Sezgin Irmak dans le rôle de Salih Çelikhan (frère aîné de Karan)
≫ Ayça Bilir dans le rôle de Aliye Olcay Çelikhan (fille de Salih et Meltem)
≫ Burak Özen dans le rôle de Emir Çelikhan (enfant adoptif d’Hikmet)
≫ Ayşegül Şen dans le rôle de Meltem Olcay (liaison secrète de Salih)

𝙲𝚑𝚊𝚗𝚗𝚎𝚕 𝚖𝚊𝚗𝚊𝚐𝚎𝚍 𝚋𝚢 𝚃𝚞𝚛𝚗𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝚁𝚎𝚍 𝙼𝚎𝚍𝚒𝚊𝚌𝚘𝚛𝚙 𝚘𝚗 𝚋𝚎𝚑𝚊𝚕𝚏 𝚘𝚏 𝙶𝚘𝚚𝚞𝚎𝚜𝚝 𝙼𝚎𝚍𝚒𝚊 𝚞𝚗𝚍𝚎𝚛 𝚘𝚞𝚛 “𝚈𝚘𝚞𝚃𝚞𝚋𝚎 𝙵𝚒𝚛𝚜𝚝” 𝚒𝚗𝚒𝚝𝚒𝚊𝚝𝚒𝚟𝚎.

snippet.title: Honest Trailers | The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King
snippet.description:
It’s the Honest Trailer for The Lord of the Rings: The Return of The King! After an extended edition sized sabbatical in the woods, Aragon has been given a return to office notice or else he’ll lose his job as the king of all mankind. While The King makes his return, the hobbits return the ring to sender for a full refund, minus shipping and handling (fingering?). It’s the perfect ending to the perfect trilogy, and then it keeps going for another 15-20 minutes but we don’t want it to be over either.

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)
Title Design: Robert Holtby

Produced by: Spencer Gilbert
Edited by: Kevin Williamsen

snippet.title: Anime “Dragon Ball Super: Beerus” | SUPER Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Series Premieres in Fall of 2026!
The anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus in Fall 2026!

#dragonball #dragonballsuper

◾️INTRODUCTION
The globally beloved manga DRAGON BALL by Akira Toriyama continues to captivate fans through a wide range of media—from TV animation, movies, games, and merchandising—standing as a top-ranked title with extraordinary worldwide popularity. 
Now, in 2026, the anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus! This ENHANCED edition introduces a large volume of newly added and redrawn cuts, as well as a reconstructed narrative. With cutting-edge visual expression, the series delivers even more immersive battle scenes and a more faithful representation of the original manga—bringing an ENHANCED edition to life like never before.

Several years have passed since the fierce battle against Majin Buu, and Earth has finally regained a brief moment of peace. At the same time, Beerus, the God of Destruction, awakens from his long, deep sleep. Even Kai and Supreme Kai, aware of Beerus’s overwhelming power to destroy entire planets, watch his awakening with great fear… Meanwhile, Beerus hears rumors of a Saiyan who defeated Frieza—and suddenly appears before Goku.
Targeted by Beerus, the strongest being in the universe, Earth is in grave danger. Thus begins an Earth-shattering cosmic battle between the God of Destruction and Goku and his allies—a conflict that will shake the entire universe.

Original Work, Story & Character Design: Akira Toriyama

snippet.title: OPÉRATION : ZOMBIE DE COMPAGNIE !! -Quarantine Zone: The Last Check- [DRESSAGE ?]
snippet.description:
Attention "Au pied", il ne faut pas qu'il l'interprète de la mauvaise façon.

Quarantine Zone: The Last Check ! Une fusion potara entre Papers, Please et That's Not my Neighbor ! En pleine apocalypse zombie, vous vous retrouvez propulsé au plus haut rang d'un point de contrôle à haut risque, avec à peu près autant de formation qu'un ambulancier face à un bloc opératoire ! À vous d'utiliser vos connaissances de première année de médecine et votre technologie de pointe toute droit sortie d'un eroge pour séparer le grain bien portant de l'ivraie nécrosée ! Le jeu est enfin complet, plus chiadé et approfondi que jamais ! Plus de civils clonés aux lignes de dialogues synchonisées, plus de traductions à la fiabilité toute approximative, plus de petits chariots à pousser ou de militaires à l'indolence contre-productive ! Ça fait du bien de voir des jeux filtrer leur gameplay à l'épuisette, ça permet de pas manger trop gras.

Toujours merci à SpongePierre, miniaturiste assermenté et héros de vos coeurs.

Vous pouvez aussi m'suivre sur Twitter/X :
http://x.com/RoiLennon

Bisous et à la prochaine !

Virtual Boy - Nintendo Classics - coming to Nintendo Switch 2 and Nintendo Switch on Feb 17! 

With a Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack membership, Nintendo Switch™ and Nintendo Switch™ 2 players will be able to access a collection of Virtual Boy™ games to play anytime, anywhere! Create suspend points in each game to save your progress, rewind to fix your mistakes, and adjust the controls to suit your preferences as you bash robots in Teleroboxer™, jump between background and foreground in Virtual Boy™ Wario Land™, and more.

• Teleroboxer™
• Galactic Pinball™

snippet.title: Mbosso - Darasa La Saba (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
"Darasa La Saba" is a quiet love letter to first love and broken dreams. Two hearts meet in childhood, then life pulls them apart. Poverty, distance, and time standing in the way. As his dream of becoming a doctor fades, his search for her never does. Moving from place to place, she becomes a memory he still chases, not for the past, but for peace. It’s a song about love that grows up before it ever gets a chance to grow old, The song tells a tender story of love that grows up before it ever gets the chance to grow old. The video was shot in Bukoba region, Tanzania

طير يا طيري بلا عنوان و احكي حكياتي في كل مكان

بلاد الوتر بلاد الشجعان أرض الاولياء و البيان

شحال تمنينا و ليالي عداو و حدي فالمدينة و عدياني كيتاو 
بلى رياح السفينة صغار ديماراو

Heart beats fast
Colors and promises
How to be brave?
How can I love when I'm
Afraid to fall?

All of my doubt
Suddenly goes away somehow

One step closer
[Chorus]
I have died every day waiting for you
Darling, don't be afraid
I have loved you for a thousand years
I'll love you for a thousand more

Time stands still
Beauty in all she is
I will be brave
I will not let anything
Take away

Every breath
Every hour has come to this

One step closer

[Chorus]
I have died every day waiting for you
Darling, don't be afraid
I have loved you for a thousand years
I'll love you for a thousand more

[Bridge]
And all along I believed I would find you
Time has brought your heart to me
I have loved you for a thousand years
I'll love you for a thousand more

[Pre-Chorus]
One step closer
One step closer

[Chorus]
I have died every day waiting for you
Darling, don't be afraid
I have loved you for a thousand years
I'll love you for a thousand more

[Outro]
And all along I believed I would find you
Time has brought your heart to me
I have loved you for a thousand years
I'll love you for a thousand more
